title: Rebecca's Coffee House
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, Fast food, Take-out, Bakery, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Coffee house in South Park with a light food menu consisting of soup, sandwiches, and house-baked pastries with sometimes a couple vegan baked goods like vegan muffin. Has Wi-Fi. Hosts open mic and music events.
